John England (Banbridge) Ltd is an Irish linen company based in Banbridge, Northern Ireland.
The original company John England Textiles Ltd., was started in Belfast in 1964 by John England. The company gained a reputation for designing unique textures and colours inspired by the natural world.
In November 2012, the brand name was sold and came under common ownership with Thomas Ferguson & Co Ltd, a well known Irish linen Jacquard weaver. Since then John England has added a wide range of new innovative fabrics woven on looms with Jacquard machines.
John England has also a theatricals department offering designers fabrics for movie, television, theatre and opera productions.
